700787f-a.folder: Commerce Avenue & Butler Place, Bronx, NY
700787f-a.text:
Commerce Ave., adjoining the N.W. corner of Butler Place, showing a cemetery overgrown with weeds and tall grass. In the background is visible the spire of St. Peters P.E. Church on Westchester Ave. at the
S.E. corner of Seabury Ave.
July 25, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
